{"title":"写给妈妈","authors":["德尔马"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":12,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"写给妈妈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴民兵　德尔马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈，祖国在向我召唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召唤我去山的那边那里自由呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由在向我召唤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要哭了，亲爱的妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道如何用枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了保卫古巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死又算得了什么！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这个世界上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有许多母亲还在受苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和您从前一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的妈妈你莫要悲伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在保卫祖国的沙场上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果我算得上一名战斗员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死了又何妨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像我一样，祖国有许多儿女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在吉隆滩的战斗里他们已经就义。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您应该感到骄傲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果您的儿子作了战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫住了祖国和大旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔光孚　译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}